<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background-color: #dc2626; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; }
    .content { background-color: #f3f4f6; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px; }
    .alert { background-color: #fef3c7; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background-color: #2563eb; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .code-box { background-color: white; padding: 15px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 5px; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; }
    .code { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #2563eb; font-family: monospace; letter-spacing: 2px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 20px; }
    .expiry { background-color: #fecaca; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px; color: #7f1d1d; margin: 15px 0; }
    .warning { color: #dc2626; font-weight: bold; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1><%= appName %></h1>
      <p>Password Reset Request</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <h2>Reset Your Password</h2>

      <div class="alert">
        <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Security Notice:</strong> You recently requested to reset the password for your account. If you did not make this request, please ignore this email. Your account security is not compromised.
      </div>

      <p>We received a request to reset the password for your account. Click the button below to create a new password:</p>

      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= resetLink %>" class="button">Reset Password</a>
      </div>

      <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #666;">Or copy this link in your browser:</p>
      <p style="background-color: white; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 5px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 11px;">
        <%= resetLink %>
      </p>

      <div class="expiry">
        ‚è±Ô∏è <strong>This link expires in <%= expiryHours %> hours</strong> (at <%= expiryTime %>)
      </div>

      <div class="alert">
        <strong>Alternative Method - Use OTP:</strong>
        <p>If the link doesn't work, you can use this one-time password code instead:</p>
        <div class="code-box">
          <div class="code"><%= otpCode %></div>
          <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin: 10px 0 0 0;">Enter this code in the password reset page</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Password Security Tips:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Use a strong password with mix of uppercase, lowercase, numbers, and symbols</li>
        <li>Avoid using personal information like names or birthdays</li>
        <li>Don't reuse passwords from other accounts</li>
        <li>Make it at least 8 characters long</li>
      </ul>

      <div style="background-color: #fff7ed; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #f97316; margin: 20px 0;">
        <strong style="color: #c2410c;">‚ö†Ô∏è Important:</strong>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;">Never share your password or reset link with anyone. Our team will never ask for your password.</p>
      </div>

      <h3>Need Help?</h3>
      <p>If you need further assistance, please contact us at:</p>
      <p>üìß <strong><%= supportEmail %></strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p><%= appName %> - Medical Pharmacy Management System</p>
      <p>This is an automated email. Please do not reply to this message.</p>
      <p>If you did not request this, please contact support immediately.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
